{"prompt": "Build an elegant website for a fine dining restaurant. The design should prominently display a refined chocolate brown.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>The Gilded Spoon</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #2e1a0e; /* Deep chocolate brown */\n            color: #f5f5dc; /* Creamy beige */\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #4a2e1a; /* Slightly lighter brown */\n            color: #f5f5dc;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #f5f5dc;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        header p {\n            margin: 5px 0 0;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #2e1a0e;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5dc;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #f5f5dc;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #d4af37; /* Gold accent on hover */\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #d4af37; /* Gold accent */\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n        .menu-item {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(245, 245, 220, 0.3); /* Subtle beige border */\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 30%;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            vertical-align: top;\n            margin-left: 1%;\n            margin-right: 1%;\n        }\n        .menu-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #d4af37;\n        }\n        .menu-item h3 {\n            margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: #d4af37; /* Gold accent */\n        }\n        .menu-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        #about {\n            background-color: #4a2e1a; /* Slightly lighter brown */\n            color: #f5f5dc;\n        }\n        #about p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        #contact {\n            background-color: #2e1a0e;\n            color: #f5f5dc;\n        }\n        #contact p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        #contact a {\n            color: #d4af37;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        #contact a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #4a2e1a; /* Slightly lighter brown */\n            color: #f5f5dc;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .smooth-scroll {\n            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;\n        }\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; }\n            to { opacity: 1; }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>The Gilded Spoon</h1>\n        <p>An Exquisite Culinary Experience</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#menu\">Menu</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"menu\" class=\"container smooth-scroll\">\n        <h2>Our Signature Dishes</h2>\n        <div class=\"menu-item\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a2e1a/f5f5dc?text=Seared+Scallops\" alt=\"Seared Scallops\">\n            <h3>Pan-Seared Sea Scallops</h3>\n            <p>Delicate scallops with a lemon-butter sauce, served over a bed of saffron risotto.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"menu-item\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a2e1a/f5f5dc?text=Filet+Mignon\" alt=\"Filet Mignon\">\n            <h3>Truffle-Infused Filet Mignon</h3>\n            <p>Prime cut filet mignon with a rich black truffle reduction and roasted asparagus.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"menu-item\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a2e1a/f5f5dc?text=Chocolate+Lava+Cake\" alt=\"Chocolate Lava Cake\">\n            <h3>Molten Chocolate Lava Cake</h3>\n            <p>Warm, decadent chocolate cake with a gooey center, served with raspberry coulis.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container smooth-scroll\">\n        <h2>About The Gilded Spoon</h2>\n        <p>Established in the heart of the city, The Gilded Spoon offers an unparalleled fine dining experience. Our chefs meticulously craft each dish using the finest seasonal ingredients, paired with an extensive wine list curated to complement every palate. We invite you to indulge in an evening of sophisticated flavors and impeccable service.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container smooth-scroll\">\n        <h2>Visit Us</h2>\n        <p>123 Culinary Lane, Gastronomy City</p>\n        <p>Reservations: <a href=\"tel:+15551234567\">(555) 123-4567</a></p>\n        <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:reservations@gildedspoon.com\">reservations@gildedspoon.com</a></p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 The Gilded Spoon. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}